Ensure completion of training KPIs.
Internal communication about training
In charge of articles related to internal training activities of the Group;
Building and spreading training culture in the Ecosystem (Live, Online);
Have a marketing strategy for the program so that a large number of employees can participate.
Invite more speakers, instructors if necessary.
Other tasks.
Participating in the creativity and coordination of internal events of the Human Resources Division;
Other duties as required by the Direct Manager.

